{"tid":1922860,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾晤確診巴西總統新聞秘書　美國總統特朗普稱不擔心","createTime":"2020-03-12T20:53:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T23:28:41.000Z","uid":125193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dd11f85d3e18aa280d620342d532363350cd9ba7","tid":1922860,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T20:53:01.000Z","msg":"巴西總統博爾索納羅的新聞秘書，對新型冠狀病毒呈陽性反應，這位新聞秘書上周末曾經在佛羅里達州海湖莊園，與美國總統特朗普見面，並曾經一同用餐，美國副總統彭斯當時亦在場。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮與愛爾蘭總理瓦拉德卡會面後，表示並不擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">白宮發表聲明，指特朗普與彭斯幾乎並無與這名新聞秘書互動，目前毋須進行病毒測試。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514133-20200313.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514133-20200313.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BPZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=cab78daf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514133-20200313.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dd905736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514133-20200313.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4cabe7c2b10a3513def04c8f1d3b8ea4c1681824","tid":1922860,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T20:53:17.000Z","msg":"wtf........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5001e3b37ec6fffa9cdf7df60cf8ede145f7d8","tid":1922860,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T20:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj